Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎮壓亞古捷斯的古利明艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與姬娜的艦隊開始交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著戰鬥空域廣大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加碼陷入了危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時程為盾牌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一直想與布拉度艦長見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.65,0:01:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我犯下不可挽回的大錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十五話\n亞古捷斯的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜已率領友軍艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去亞古捷斯去討伐古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在其後方支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是成為\n奪回亞古捷斯的先鋒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可小看敵人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的新人類部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠比高達隊伍更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉的勇者們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了獲得勇者名聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人也不可\n對古利明軍手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算對手是你過去的戰友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.80,0:02:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命運一定會給哈曼大人\n帶來輝煌的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡有惡報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.45,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罪惡必受懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.79,0:02:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種情況的洗腦作業\n倒是做的很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.26,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡有惡報,犯罪必受懲罰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要欺騙自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就必須先與自己人同化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.79,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果說這是骯髒的血統\n我也只好承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是下次見面時\n我一定要取下你的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我這雙手來重建吉翁王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球聯邦軍的援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎不打算進入三號殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道他們想漁翁得利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已被我們新人類的意識控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人不會進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨終的時刻已過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬惡的根源就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪走美莉芭殿下的哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能掌握新吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是將哈曼的人頭獻上來給我的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時你們將成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後代口中的宇宙英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個黃毛小子真會演講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們拿哈曼的人頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是要給我們一個殖民地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說要給我們地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡你啊,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是在討你歡心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.62,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於昨天還對哈曼誓忠的人\n至少要有送他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個地球的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想把我們的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塗成那麼難看的顏色嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是古利明大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說為了新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.97,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要團結在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想壓制浮動的士氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個主意是不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,我是例外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接給古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.43,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達卡恩大人要與你談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.59,0:05:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,達卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多賓野狼\n的確是只有我軍才有的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.43,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小事隨時可能會弄死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然這麼在意外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別撞上攝影機啊,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從拉比安羅茲回收過來的零件\n快點修理好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倉庫已經滿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不裝上去以後會很難收拾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在乾脆丟掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莉的意思是那些都是必需品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些東西在戰鬥時只會礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說呢,奇斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲的黑盒子\n一定要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.74,0:06:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有艾美莉代理艦長\n生前的最後遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑盒子太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錄有艾美莉聲音的磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放心吧,艾美莉代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會交到\n布拉度艦長手上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣有點沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是空調故障了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候還說笑\n你這是什麼個性啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不可小看的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我問你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲傷就能讓死人復活的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的事情早點忘記是好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人一死就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們以後我們還得活下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這種人最容易早死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊,莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百式的維修工作還沒好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等一會再去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪不可能不傷心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也剛失去重要的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說拉莎拉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定他比米莉更傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,捷度呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說等一會過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不自己照顧可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能太指望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球聯邦的援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.72,0:08:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明下次從亞古捷斯出來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.23,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會當作沒看見\n我們去打哈曼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那時候\n我們從側面攻擊古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再戰哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能瞄準旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁開始活動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對  哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在把古利明當成敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但沒人能保證\n哈曼會再艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也沒人能保證\n哈曼不在那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之不管怎樣\n哈曼必定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全力攻擊亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能從後面追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在後面旁觀戰況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就能知道哈曼打的主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,哈曼在那艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度到底支持哪邊的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道嗎?\n捷度想和哈曼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的了結啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的了結?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是某一方會死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的想法太極端了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古時候的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍人出陣前會遠離身邊的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與自己的武器共渡一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,阿斯蘭治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天怎麼這麼老實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新裝甲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,這是把浮走粒子做成漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複烤漆好幾層的裝甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光波擊中它會被反彈開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.67,0:10:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是光波若是持續三秒以上\n漆就會融化掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是新吉翁軍的宇宙要塞\n亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再放出假隕石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發呆\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你們別發呆啊\n快跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吧,尼伊,藍斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲在假隕石的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做不成大事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達卡恩,急於立功會出錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要拿下古利明人頭的\n是我馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗腦很成功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,安多拉的勇者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天這一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新吉翁的最佳一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明是叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家跟隨我去打倒他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.65,0:12:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人忠實的僕人\n去開出血路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要讓哈曼看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明不是我的對手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺到力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場仗我贏定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒那麼痛快了,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩架MS是姬娜的親衛隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,壞一架\n應該是達卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我多賓野狼的厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩這個把戲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.63,0:13:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲的真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點程度不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要自大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?這是什麼壓力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是從哪裏來的?那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜嗎?不,不是\n是馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然不要命的跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道害怕的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文挺能打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你玩了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙不是常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難分出勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會變成長期戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出結論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也幫忙擊敗亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然背後受到攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,準備戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很惹人厭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查你怎會這麼好心\n肯和我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我平常也是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是某人過去的心不在身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有注意到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種話我不會說兩次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧,大家都在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...活著回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再對我說一次好嗎?比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩護高達隊伍出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能活著回香格里拉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能的,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,達卡恩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,給我看看你的本領吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別像你手下那樣逃跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的背上沒有光波炮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太天真了,達卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你為何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像聽到捷度的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了? 姬娜\n又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貓女姬娜怎麼可能被打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是ZZ高達怎麼會再那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是來還上次的人情債啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很記恩的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了,又傳來捷度的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了\n別大聲叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會頭痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏?姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我頭痛了,別管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏\n姬娜大人就不對勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世被壓制了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要一口氣衝進去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明還沒使出全力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要假裝撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引出他的戰力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你上當了\n馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種騙小孩的玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓你乾脆死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心\n下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被彈回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你動了什麼手腳?馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會失敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.48,0:20:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會戰到死為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快脫離啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼光芒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?是誰死了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來出去時的氣勢\n只是裝出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強化過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.38,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就少掉一個\n可以隨意控制的棋子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,你要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.63,0:21:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同一招對付不了那個駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要替馬士文報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是命令,立刻回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人就在眼前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS戰不利的古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.62,0:23:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試圖用亞古捷斯和哈曼的艦隊碰撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要與古利明和波蕾二世對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是被他們兩個壓制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾來救我了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對 是波蕾二世？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.97,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,共震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.68,0:24:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世 太勉強了！

